    13→
    14→/**
    15→ * RecurrencePicker Component
    16→ * UI for setting up recurring task patterns
    17→ *
    18→ * Features:
    19→ * - Frequency selection (daily, weekly, monthly, yearly)
    20→ * - Interval input (every X days/weeks/months/years)
    21→ * - Day of week picker (for weekly)
    22→ * - Day of month picker (for monthly)
